metadata.description: Welcome to Club101. This is a C101 Member Access Pass (MAP). It provides basic Club 101 Membership. Club 101 is a Web3 Business Club based around 5 Pillars:IDO RADs (Random AirDrops), Metaverse Expansion, Intellectual Property Development & Partnerships, Den of Dragons Services, Tools, Resources, & Education Access. The higher tier memberships (Diamond, Sapphire, & Gold Dragon) have their own collections, found through Official Links in our Discord, & give greater access to our events and properties (such as limited entry into our Ethereum Towers Penthouse Dragons Opportunity, Events & Business Development Courses & Resources). For more information check out our website at https://club101.io/ or join our Discord at https://discord.gg/Club101
